{
  "stem": "16163.1",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] the trouble we got into is that we come from a small little hilly town.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we found, naturally, the highest little mountain there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We would climb up there in dangerous positions, and things like this, and just got-- you know, like little troubles.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They were glad we came home in one piece.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When I was a child-- now, it became a bigger town, because they incorporated a lot of small towns.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was a small town with 5,000 people living there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And what I remember, there were never more than 20 Jewish families in town.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And little by little in the beginning, some people moved, and immigrated to the states, or somewhere else.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So by the time that I really remember, there were maybe 10 families left, at the most.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, I had this one boy.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "His name was Gunter Katz.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he was survived also Auschwitz, et cetera.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he never came back to Vlotho.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He was sent from Vlotho to Holland.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "From Holland, he came to Theresienstadt, from Theresienstadt to Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And when he was liberated, I don't know where he was liberated, the Russians took him to Odessa, and flew him back to Holland.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And from in Holland, he found out that none of his family except one aunt survived.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And she was in Belgium.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So she went to-- he went to Brussels to meet her there, and then came to the United States.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But he passed away here.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, yes, yes.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, he got in touch with us.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't know how come he got our address.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I think he found out through one of the organizations that my mother and I were the only survivors who came back from Vlotho.",
      "word_count": 24
    }
  ],
